      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used under vendor-supplied V&V documentation; FDA in-house FEA code maintained under a documented software quality plan consistent with 21 CFR Part 11.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA solvers (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under documented software quality assurance programs. Ansys is a commercially validated solver; FDA in-house code is maintained under a formal SQA plan. Required level 2 achieved."
