      "rationale": "A systematic mesh convergence study was performed across three mesh refinement levels. Richardson extrapolation yielded GCI values below 2% for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm. Required level 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative solver residuals below 1e-6 for all load steps; energy balance checked at each increment.",
      "rationale": "Nonlinear solution convergence was monitored via force and displacement residuals. All analyses converged to residuals below 1e-6. Energy balance confirmed at each load increment. Required level 2 achieved."
