      "rationale": "The validation activity directly replicates the ASTM F1717 static compression-bending protocol specified in the regulatory submission. The validated construct geometry, material, and loading are identical to the COU. This one-to-one correspondence between validation scenario and COU maximizes relevance. Required level 3 achieved."
    }
